General.Name: Triton International Group Inc
General.Description: Triton International Limited engages in the acquisition, leasing, re-leasing, and sale of various types of intermodal containers and chassis to shipping lines, and freight forwarding companies and manufacturers. It operates in two segments, Equipment Leasing and Equipment Trading. The company primarily leases dry, refrigerated, special, and tank containers; and chassis used for the transportation of containers, as well as provides maritime container management services. As of December 31, 2022, its total fleet consisted of 4.2 million containers and chassis representing 7.2 million twenty-foot equivalent units or 7.9 million cost equivalent units. The company also purchases containers from container manufacturers, shipping line customers, and other sellers, as well as resells these containers to container retailers and users. It operates in Asia, Europe, the Americas, Bermuda, and internationally. The company was founded in 1980 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda.
